#bold[#magenta[Extended usage information:]]

  Disable options wiht #cyan[--no-option] e.g. #cyan[--no-connect]

  #bold[connect]]

    #cyan[--connect-screen]
      Open Steroids Connect screen in a separate browser window. (Default: true)

    #cyan[--livereload]
      Use (experimental) live reloading. (Default: false)

    #cyan[--watch <path>]
      Watch additional directories for changes. (Default: '')

    #cyan[--watchExclude <matcher>]
      Ignore files from watching. (Default: '')